# AppKit menu bar

## Status bar

- Icon via `CodexBrandIcon.mark()` (template image from bundled `MenuBarIcon` assets); fallback to drawn status dot.
- Status states: `AppStatus` (idle, loading, error, offline) with accessibility labels.
- Menu header shows `CodexBar {AppVersion.display}`.
- Actions: Dashboard (native window), Restart Codex, Quit.
- Restart Codex from the menu must show confirmation before restarting Codex Desktop.
- Reset Gateway Config lives in the Dashboard and must show confirmation before resetting and restarting Codex.

## App delegate

- `GatewayServer.shared.start()` on launch, `stop()` on terminate.
- Health polling via `APIClient.fetchStatus()` every 5s.
- Standard Edit menu for text fields.

## After changing menu bar or delegate

Run `make test` if logic changed; update `ARCHITECTURE.md` and `README.md` for user-visible behavior. See `docs-and-tests.mdc`.
